data.title: DEJ Productions
data.text:
1st Logo

(May 1, 1998-2003)

<embed allowfullscreen="true" height="205" src="http://wikifoundrytools.com/wiki/closinglogos/widget/youtubevideo/4d055d00b0627cd5496cdb38868ffe644fcf104d" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" width="248" wmode="transparent"/>

Nicknames: "The Ancient Babylonian Statue", "Shedu"

Logo: On a black background, we see a stylized yellow rendering of an ancient Babylonian statue. The statue depicts a Shedu, a winged bull or lion with a human head. Below it is the text "DEJ PRODUCTIONS".

FX/SFX: Only the fading.

Music/Sounds: None.

Availability: Extremely rare, but it can be found on Windfall and Savage Messiah. More common on trailers.

Editor's Note: None.
